TITLE: Setting CSP Header without Nonces in Next.js Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to set a Content Security Policy header directly in the next.config.js file without using nonces. It defines a CSP header and applies it to all routes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextjsargentina/next.js-docs/blob/main/src/docs/02-app/01-building-your-application/07-configuring/15-content-security-policy.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_3

