TITLE: Implementing Redirects in getStaticProps
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to implement redirects from getStaticProps. This allows conditionally redirecting users based on data fetched during static generation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextjsargentina/next.js-docs/blob/main/src/docs/03-pages/02-api-reference/02-functions/get-static-props.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
export async function getStaticProps(context) {
  const res = await fetch(`https://...`)
  const data = await res.json()

  if (!data) {
    return {
      redirect: {
        destination: '/',
        permanent: false,
        // statusCode: 301
      },
    }
  }

  return {
    props: { data }, // will be passed to the page component as props
  }
}
```

