TITLE: Sirv Loader Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Custom image loader implementation for Sirv dynamic imaging service
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextjsargentina/next.js-docs/blob/main/src/docs/02-app/02-api-reference/05-next-config-js/images.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
export default function sirvLoader({ src, width, quality }) {
  const url = new URL(`https://example.com${src}`)
  const params = url.searchParams
  params.set('format', params.getAll('format').join(',') || 'optimal')
  params.set('w', params.get('w') || width.toString())
  params.set('q', (quality || 85).toString())
  return url.href
}
```

